59
00:02:09,670 --> 00:02:13,689
a Taiwanese activist to five years in prison.

60
00:02:13,689 --> 00:02:16,349
We talked about Lee Ming-che back in September.

61
00:02:16,349 --> 00:02:18,379
Well this week he was found guilty

62
00:02:18,379 --> 00:02:20,439
of “subverting state power”

63
00:02:20,439 --> 00:02:22,079
