88
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:27,279
with Chinese characteristics.

89
00:03:27,279 --> 00:03:29,790
Chinese tech giant Tencent has bought the
rights

90
00:03:29,790 --> 00:03:31,709
to bring PUBG to China.

91
00:03:31,709 --> 00:03:33,620
And they’ve agreed to make some changes

92
00:03:33,620 --> 00:03:36,730
